SHA256sum: b5cce67a72d21e19ad0fea21f7957a14dd8a1f8e1d5a1b1fe5857a51bae081b4
Description:  gmpy2 is a C-coded Python extension module that supports multiple-precision
 arithmetic. gmpy2 is the successor to the original gmpy module. The gmpy module
 only supported the GMP multiple-precision library. gmpy2 adds support for the
 MPFR (correctly rounded real floating-point arithmetic) and MPC (correctly
 rounded complex floating-point arithmetic) libraries. gmpy2 also updates the
 API and naming conventions to be more consistent and support the additional
 functionality.
 
 This package contains the Python source files for python3-gmpy2.

