Package: python3-mutagen-src
Version: 1.46.0-r1
Depends: libc
Source: feeds/packages/lang/python/python-mutagen
SourceName: python-mutagen
License: GPL-2.0-or-later
LicenseFiles: COPYING
Section: lang
SourceDateEpoch: 1761595978
URL: https://mutagen.readthedocs.io/
Maintainer: Tianling Shen <cnsztl@immortalwrt.org>
Architecture: mipsel_24kc
Installed-Size: 645120
Filename: python3-mutagen-src_1.46.0-r1_mipsel_24kc.ipk
Size: 139553
SHA256sum: 45fea3beed5a3fba2a1bfec76021cbdb0b14c87b347ee1c525c1ca599f66a019
Description:  Mutagen is a Python module to handle audio metadata.
 
 It supports ASF, FLAC, MP4, Monkey's Audio, MP3, Musepack, Ogg Opus,
 Ogg FLAC, Ogg Speex, Ogg Theora, Ogg Vorbis, True Audio, WavPack,
 OptimFROG, and AIFF audio files.
 
 All versions of ID3v2 are supported, and all standard ID3v2.4 frames
 are parsed. It can read Xing headers to accurately calculate the
 bitrate and length of MP3s. ID3 and APEv2 tags can be edited regardless
 of audio format. It can also manipulate Ogg streams on an individual
 packet/page level.
 
 This package contains the Python source files for python3-mutagen.

